cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper is primarily focused on data center networks, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the replication mechanism for maintaining file lifetime and data security, which is related to Networked and Internet-based Systems (cs.NI) and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). The proposed methods for assessing file lifetime and data security involve Markov processes, which is related to Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Information Theory (cs.IT).
